        "created_at": "2025-08-28T08:43:09.129Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Maybe the link and sync resumes after a restart <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/thinking.png?v=14\" title=\":thinking:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":thinking:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Not sure but worth a try</p>\n<p>And I believe a newly set up desktop linked device asks if you’d like to import or start over fresh, so definitely could try to sync back your history to desktop if not present</p>",
